      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      58.92,
      247.05,
      558.16,
      261.36
    ],
    "text": "Act (Amended ) No.20 of 1991. The charge sheet was filed on the 13th of July 2015, on the same day",
